high_descs: Go forward to the counter on your right, to the left of the sink, and face the counter.
Pick up the fork that is to the left of the sink.
Carry the fork to the counter on the right side of the sink.
Put the fork, handle-first, into the green glass on the counter.
Pick up the glass with the fork in it.
Take the glass with the fork to the sink.
Put the glass with the fork in the left front corner of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a green glass containing a fork into the sink.

high_descs: Go right and stand at the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick the fork up off of the counter.
Go right and stand in front of the counter to the right of the sink and pick the fork up.
Put the fork in the green cup.
Pick the cup up from the counter.
Go left and stand in front of the sink.
Put the cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a fork in it in the sink.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then turn right to face the end of the kitchen island.
Pick up the metal fork that is on the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk to the other side of the kitchen island where the golden statue is resting.
Place the metal fork into the green cup that is to the left of the golden statue.
Pick up the green cup with the metal fork in it.
Turn left and walk over to the sink that is in the middle of the kitchen island.
Place the green cup with the metal fork in it into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a green cup with a metal fork in it into the sink basin.
